    "Toast listed on the New York Stock Exchange in a 2021 IPO that was the largest ever by a Boston-based company.",
    "Fredette and his cofounders, Aman Narang and Jonathan Grimm, attended MIT and worked at Cambridge, Massachusetts-based search software company Endeca together.",
